\PERSONA: LAERTES, son to Polonius.
\PERSONA: LUCIANUS, nephew to the king.

\PGROUP<
\PERSONA: VOLTIMAND
\PERSONA: CORNELIUS
\PERSONA: ROSENCRANTZ
\PERSONA: GUILDENSTERN
\PERSONA: OSRIC
\GRPDESCR: courtiers.
>

\PERSONA: A Gentleman
\PERSONA: A Priest. 

\PGROUP<
\PERSONA: MARCELLUS
\PERSONA: BERNARDO
\GRPDESCR: officers.
>

\PERSONA: FRANCISCO, a soldier.
\PERSONA: REYNALDO, servant to Polonius.
\PERSONA: Players.
\PERSONA: Two Clowns, grave-diggers.
\PERSONA: FORTINBRAS, prince of Norway. 
\PERSONA: A Captain.
\PERSONA: English Ambassadors. 
